    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情设定为未来的一次地外生命调查，某星球的探测器传回了生命反应并接收到求救信息，随后便失去联系，于是玩家将扮演一队调查人员，前往目标星球调查情况，在调查过程中意外进入未知文明领地，遭遇怪异生物袭击，请尽力生存下去，并等待救援</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法就是传统的FPS+闯关，玩家进入地图后，地图中会出现地点提示，玩家需要到达指定地点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/f088f6573a79593508f11f62044c3679.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而在探索地图的过程中，会出现很多敌人，用武器射击敌人确保生存，最终完成所有任务，到达指定地点即可通关</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/16705fa92b8690e8fcdf732139e7bdc4.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >途中会有一些特殊敌人，注意优先击杀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.poster.avif?t=1731999259\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.webm?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237440/extras/ab835905c0e2f8d19a1a82e74f337fea.mp4?t=1731999259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内的子弹设定为能量补充，所以不用担心弹药问题，最后还有一些道具，同样也是消耗能量来补充使用。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >素材表</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D模型：虚幻商店/Cgtrader/Artstation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作动画：虚幻商店/Mixamo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >图片：虚幻商店/Deviantart</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其余素材均来自虚幻商店</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于只有单人制作，有很多想法因为人力原因无法实现，开始并不是只想做成简单的射击闯关类型，后面可能会加入对抗模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时间大概为1小时左右（在不通关多难度的情况下），也请把游戏中遇到的一些bug和建议写成评论，以便后续更新修复，最后感谢您的游玩</p>",
